Check Free Banking

Bank more, worry less with your account.

We understand that your needs may be different from your closest friends or family members. That’s why we give you the choice of a primary banking account that is checkless, has no overdraft or non-sufficient funds fees and includes mobile budgeting apps.

$0

Minimum Balance
$25 minimum deposit to open

$5

Maintenance Fee1

Contact a Personal Banker or visit a local banking center to get started.

Find a Banker

You'll also have access to these great services:

Financial Team

Achieve your financial goals with the help of our team of financial experts.

Learn More

Online Banking

Check balances and manage accounts day and night from any device.

Learn More

Savvy Money Management

Centralize your finances to track spending, set financial goals and monitors all of your accounts.

Learn More

You may also be interested in:

Personal Loans

New car, your next adventure, an R/V for family road trips - whatever your needs we have financing options for you.

See More

Personal Account Fee Schedule

1Must enroll in statements within the first 30 days of account opening or account conversion. If eStatements are discontinued, then a Paper Statement fee of $2.00 would apply.
